anfeelingg00buzz|url-access=registration|page=[https://archive.org/details/badwomanfeelingg00buzz/page/264 264]|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last=Jung|first=K. Elan|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=uQ2I9cpJWYIC&pg=PA188#v=onepage|title=Sexual Trauma: A Challenge Not Insanity|publisher=The Hudson Press|year=2010|isbn=978-0-9831448-0-9|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last=Klaffke|first=Pamela|title=Spree: A Cultural History of Shopping|year=2003|location=Vancouver|publisher=Arsenal Pulp Press|isbn=978-1-55152-143-5|ref=harv|url=https://archive.org/details/spree00pame}}\n* {{cite book|first1=Molly|last1=Ladd-Taylor|first2=Lauri|last2=Umanski|title=Bad Mothers: The Politics of Blame in Twentieth-Century America|year=1998|isbn=978-0-8147-5120-6|location=New York|publisher=NYU Press|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last=Lankford|first=Ronald D. Jr.|title=Women Singer-Songwriters in Rock: A Populist Rebellion in the 1990s|location=Lanham|publisher=Scarecrow Press|year=2009|isbn=978-0-8108-7268-4|ref=harv|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=9tfTBa5ZQoAC&printsec=frontcover}}\n* {{cite book|last=Latham|first=David|title=Haunted Texts: Studies in Pre-Raphaelitism in Honour of William E. Fredeman|year=2003|publisher=University of Toronto Press|isbn=978-0-8020-3662-9|ref=harv|url=https://books.google.com/books/about/Haunted_Texts.html?id=R81qhmUO2BoC}}\n* {{cite book |editor-last=Levy |editor-first=Joe |title=The 500 Greatest Albums of All Time|year=2005|publisher=Wenner|isbn=978-1-932958-01-0|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last=Love|first=Courtney|title=Dirty Blonde: The Diaries of Courtney Love|location=London|publisher=Picador|year=2006|isbn=978-0-330-44546-7|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite journal|last=Marks|first=Craig|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=oJSpnH7TRHsC&pg=PA46#v=onepage|title=Endless Love|journal=Spin|volume=10|date=February 1995|issue=11|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |editor-last=Millard |editor-first=Andr\u00e9 |title=The Electric Guitar: A History of an American Icon|url=https://books.google.com/?id=zUlt7Q71_ssC&pg=PA195|location=Baltimore|publisher=Johns Hopkins University Press|isbn=978-0-8018-7862-6|year=2004|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|title=Girl Culture: An Encyclopedia (Two Volumes)|first1=Claudia|last1=Mitchell|first2=Jacqueline|last2=Reid-Walsh|publisher=Greenwood Publishing|isbn=978-0-313-33908-0|year=2007|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite journal|last=Nicolini|first=Kim|url=http://bad.eserver.org/issues/1995/20/nicolini.html|journal=Bad Subjects|title=Staging the Slut: Hyper-Sexuality in Performance|year=1995|issue=20|ref=harv|access-date=October 29, 2011|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071022062320/http://bad.eserver.org/issues/1995/20/nicolini.html|archive-date=October 22, 2007|url-status=dead|df=mdy-all}}\n*{{cite book|last=O'Dair|first=Barbara|year=1997|title=Trouble Girls: The Rolling Stone Book of Women in Rock|url=https://archive.org/details/troublegirlsroll00odai|url-access=registration|publisher=Random House|location=New York|ref=harv|isbn=978-0-679-76874-6}}\n* {{cite book|last=Raha|first=Maria |author-link=Maria Raha|year=2004|title=Cinderella's Big Score: Women of the Punk and Indie Underground|publisher=Seal Press|isbn=978-1-58005-116-3|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite journal|last=Raphael|first=Amy |date=March 4, 1995|journal=NME|title=While My Guitar Gently Weeps|pages=16\u201317, 67|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last=Raphael|first=Amy|title=Grrrls: Viva Rock Divas|location=New York|publisher=St. Martin's Griffin|year=1996|isbn=978-0-312-14109-7|ref=harv|url=https://archive.org/details/grrrlsvivarockdi00raph}}\n* {{cite book|first1=Dafydd|last1=Rees|first2=Luke|last2=Crampton|title=Rock Stars Encyclopedia|year=1999|location=London|publisher=DK Pub.|isbn=978-0-7894-4613-8|ref=harv|url=https://archive.org/details/rockstarsencyclo00rees}}\n* {{cite book|last=Reisfeld|first=Randi|url=https://books.google.com/?id=MdmBYULpTrAC&pg=PT77|title=This Is the Sound: The Best of Alternative Rock|location=New York|publisher=Aladdin|isbn=978-0-689-80670-4|year=1996|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|ref={{SfnRef|Rocco|Rocco|1999}} |title=Dead Reckonings: The Life and Times of the Grateful Dead |url=https://archive.org/details/isbn_9780028648965 |url-access=registration |year=1999 |location=New York |publisher=Schirmer |isbn=978-0-8256-7174-6 |editor1=Rocco, John M. |editor2=Rocco, Brian}}\n* {{cite book|last=Rogatis|first=Jim|title=Milk It!: Collected Musings on the Alternative Music Explosion of the 90s|url=https://books.google.com/?id=LXNUWWuzscMC&pg=PA128|location=Cambridge, Massachusetts|publisher=Da Capo Press|year=2003|isbn=978-0-306-81271-2|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last=Roshan|first=Maer|year=2012|location=New York|publisher=[[Sterling Publishing|Sterling]]|title=Courtney Comes Clean: The High Life and Dark Depths of Music's Most Controversial Icon|isbn=978-1-4027-9791-0|series=A Quick Fix Book|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last=Schippers|first=Mimi A.|title=Rockin' out of the Box: Gender Maneuvering in Alternative Hard Rock|publisher=Rutgers University Press|year=2002|isbn=978-0-8135-3075-8|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last=Surmani|first=Karen Farnum|url=https://books.google.com/?id=rwgKbnccWJMC&pg=PA4|series=Basix|isbn=978-0-88284-763-4|year=1997|title=Rock Singing Techniques|location=Van Nuys, California|publisher=Alfred Music|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last=Yadao|first=Jason S.|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=8h5oC4SWfC8C&pg=PA54#v=onepage|title=The Rough Guide to Manga|location=New York; London|publisher=Penguin|year=2009|series=Rough Guides|isbn=978-1-85828-561-0|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite AV media|people=Yapp, Will (dir.)|date=September 26, 2006|title=[[The Return of Courtney Love]]|medium=Documentary|location=Los Angeles|publisher=Channel 4|ref={{sfnref|Yapp|2006}}}}\n* {{cite book|last=Yarm|first=Mark|title=Everybody Loves Our Town: An Oral History of Grunge|isbn=978-0-307-46444-6|location=New York|publisher=Three Rivers Press|year=2011|ref=harv|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=z-44p7V2TrUC&printsec=frontcover