, Imagine Dragons and Martin Bandier Honored at BMI's 67th Annual Pop Awards|date=May 15, 2019 |publisher=[[Broadcast Music, Inc.|BMI]] |access-date=May 15, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[BET Awards 2019|BET Awards]]\n| Best Collaboration\n| {{nom}}\n| style=\"text-align:center; \"rowspan=\"2\"|<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.bet.com/shows/bet-awards/nominees.html|title=  The 2019 BET Awards nominations|date=May 17, 2019 }}</ref>\n|-\n| Coca-Cola Viewers' Choice Award\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[2019 MTV Millennial Awards|MTV Millennial Awards]]\n| rowspan=2| Global Hit\n| {{nominated}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref name=\"winners\">{{Cite news |url=http://www.mtvla.com/mx/mtv-miaw/noticias/estos-son-los-ganadores-de-los-premios-mtv-miaw-2019|title=Estos son los ganadores de los MTV MIAW 2019|work=MTV LA|access-date=June 22, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[MTV Millennial Awards Brazil]]\n| {{nominated}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.vagalume.com.br/news/2019/05/06/veja-os-indicados-para-o-mtv-miaw-2019.html|title=Veja os indicados para o MTV MIAW Brasil 2019|accessdate=7 May 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[ASCAP Award|ASCAP Rhythm & Soul Music Awards]]\n| Winning Song\n| {{won}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.ascap.com/news-events/awards/2019/rs-awards |title=2019 ASCAP Rhythm & Soul Music Awards |website=ASCAP |accessdate=June 21, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Broadcast Music, Inc.|BMI R&B/Hip-Hop Awards]]\n| Winning Song\n| {{won}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.bmi.com/news/entry/2019-bmi-rb-hip-hop-awards |title= Brandy Honored with the BMI President\u2019s Award at the 2019 BMI R&B/Hip-Hop Awards|date=August 30, 2019 |publisher=Broadcast Music, Inc. |access-date=August 30, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n==Track listing==\n*'''Digital download \u2013 [[Dillon Francis]] remix'''<ref name=\"dillon francis remix\">{{cite web|title=iTunes - Music - I Like It (Dillon Francis Remix) - Single by