{"title_page": "The Way I Are (Dance with Somebody)", "text_new": "{{Infobox song\n| name       = The Way I Are (Dance with Somebody)\n| cover      = Bebe rexha-the way i are (dance with somebody).jpg\n| alt        =\n| border     = yes\n| type       = single\n| artist     = [[Bebe Rexha]] featuring [[Lil Wayne]]\n| EP         = [[All Your Fault: Pt. 2]]\n| released   = {{Start date|2017|5|19}}\n| format     = [[Music download|Digital download]]\n| recorded   =\n| studio     =\n| venue      =\n| genre      = {{hlist|[[Pop music|Pop]]}}\n| length     = {{duration|m=3|s=07}}\n| label      = [[Warner Bros. Records|Warner Bros.]]\n| writer     = {{hlist|[[Bleta Rexha]]|[[Lil Wayne]]|[[Jonas Jeberg]]|[[Joel Little]]|[[The Monsters and the Strangerz|Clarence Coffee Jr.]]|[[Shannon Rubicam]]|[[George Merrill (songwriter)|George Merrill]]|Jacob Kasher}}\n| producer   = {{hlist|Joel Little|Jonas Jeberg}}\n| chronology = [[Bebe Rexha]]\n| prev_title = [[F.F.F.]]\n| prev_year  = 2017\n| next_title = [[Back to You (Louis Tomlinson song)|Back to You]]\n| next_year  = 2017\n| misc       = {{Extra chronology\n | artist     = [[Lil Wayne]]\n | type       = singles\n | prev_title = [[I'm the One (DJ Khaled song)|I'm the One]]\n | prev_year  = 2017\n | title      = The Way I Are (Dance with Somebody)\n | year       = 2017\n | next_title = [[Love U Better]]\n | next_year  = 2017\n}}\n}}\n\n\"'''The Way I Are (Dance with Somebody)'''\" is a song recorded by American singer-songwriter [[Bebe Rexha]] featuring American rapper [[Lil Wayne]], from her third [[extended play]] (EP) ''[[All Your Fault: Pt. 2]]''. It was released on  May 19, 2017 by [[Warner Bros. Records]] as the lead single from the EP.<ref name=\":2\">{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/the-way-i-are-dance-with-somebody-feat-lil-wayne-single/id1232411133|title=The Way I Are (Dance with Somebody) [feat. Lil Wayne] - Single by Bebe Rexha|work=[[iTunes Store]]|date=May 19, 2017|accessdate=May 18, 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rap-up.com/2017/05/18/new-music-bebe-rexha-lil-wayne-the-way-i-are-dance-with-somebody/|title=New Music: Bebe Rexha feat. Lil Wayne \u2013 'The Way I Are (Dance With Somebody)' |work=[[Rap-Up]]|date=May 18, 2017|accessdate=May 18, 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.idolator.com/7662867/bebe-rexha-way-i-are-cover-lil-wayne-whitney|title=Bebe Rexha Unveils The Cover Of Lil Wayne-Assisted Single 'The Way I Are'|website=Idolator|first=Mike|last=Wass|date=May 12, 2017|accessdate=May 18, 2017}}</ref> The single was leaked a week before its release, though it was deleted soon after.<ref name=\":0\">{{Cite news|url=http://www.idolator.com/7662867/bebe-rexha-way-i-are-cover-lil-wayne-whitney|title=Bebe Rexha Unveils The Cover Of New Single \"The Way I Are\"|date=2017-05-12|work=idolator|access-date=2017-05-24|language=en-US}}</ref> The single was serviced to pop radio on June 6, 2017.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://headlineplanet.com/home/2017/06/11/bebe-rexha-lil-waynes-way-dance-somebody-enters-pop-radios-top-60/|title=Bebe Rexha & Lil Wayne\u2019s \"The Way I Are (Dance With Somebody)\" Enters Pop Radio\u2019s Top 60|date=2017-06-11|work=Headline Planet|access-date=2017-06-13|language=en-US}}</ref>\n\n== Composition ==\n\"The Way I Are (Dance with Somebody)\" samples Whitney Houston's single \"[[I Wanna Dance with Somebody (Who Loves Me)|I Wanna Dance With Somebody (Who Loves Me)]]\".<ref name=\":0\" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.rap-up.com/2017/05/18/new-music-bebe-rexha-lil-wayne-the-way-i-are-dance-with-somebody/|title=New Music: Bebe Rexha feat. Lil Wayne \u2013 'The Way I Are (Dance With Somebody)'|website=Rap-Up|access-date=2017-05-24}}</ref><ref>{{Citation|title=Bebe Rexha - The Way I Are Feat. Lil Wayne {{!}} Stream [New Song]|url=http://www.hotnewhiphop.com/bebe-rexha-the-way-i-are-feat-lil-wayne-new-song.1974155.html|accessdate=2017-05-24}}</ref><ref name=\":1\">{{Cite news|url=http://www.idolator.com/7663170/bebe-rexha-way-dance-somebody-full-song-review|title=Bebe Rexha's \"The Way I Are\" Sounds Like A Summer Smash|date=2017-05-18|work=idolator|access-date=2017-05-24|language=en-US}}</ref>\n\n== Critical reception ==\nMike Wass of ''[[Idolator (website)|Idolator]]'' gave the song a positive review, calling the single \"instantly hummable and sweet relief from the endless stream of left-of-center [[Pop music|pop]] songs on radio.\"<ref name=\":1\" />\n\n== Music video ==\nThe music video directed by [[Director X]] was released on June 1, 2017. The fashion for the music video was inspired by vintage movies such as ''[[Grease (film)|Grease]]''.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/lifestyle/7817406/bebe-rexhas-stylist-on-how-to-get-her-look|title=Bebe Rexha's Stylist on How to Get Her Look in 'The Way I Are (Dance With Somebody)' Music Video: Exclusive|work=Billboard|access-date=2017-06-13}}</ref> The video features video game ''[[Just Dance 2018]]'' which the song is featured on.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2017/06/12/e3-2017-just-dance-2018-revealed|title=E3 2017: JUST DANCE 2018 REVEALED\n|access-date=2017-06-25}}</ref>\n\n== Live performances ==\nBebe Rexha and [[Lil Wayne]] performed the single together on ''[[Jimmy Kimmel Live!|Jimmy Kimmel! Live]]''.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://hiphop-n-more.com/2017/06/bebe-rexha-lil-wayne-perform-the-way-i-are-on-jimmy-kimmel-live/|title=Bebe Rexha & Lil Wayne Perform \u2018The Way I Are\u2019 On Jimmy Kimmel Live! {{!}} HipHop-N-More|date=2017-06-11|work=HipHop-N-More|access-date=2017-06-13|language=en-US}}</ref> Rexha later performed a solo version of the song on ''[[Good Morning America]]'' as part of their Summer Concert Series.\n\n== Track listing ==\n* '''Digital download'''<ref name=\"iTunes\">{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/the-way-i-are-dance-with-somebody-feat-lil-wayne/id1251713683?i=1251713722|title=The Way I Are (Dance with Somebody) [feat. Lil Wayne] - Single by Bebe Rexha|work=[[iTunes Store]]|date=May 19, 2017|accessdate=May 18, 2017}}</ref>\n{{Track listing\n| title1          = The Way I Are (Dance with Somebody)\n| note1           = featuring [[Lil Wayne]]\n| length1         = 3:08\n}}\n* '''Digital download'''<ref name=\"IT\"\">{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/the-way-i-are-dance-with-somebody/id1258191967?i=1258191968|title=The Way I Are (Dance with Somebody) - Single by Bebe Rexha|work=[[iTunes Store]]|date=July 16, 2017|accessdate=July 14, 2017}}</ref>\n{{Track listing\n| title1          = The Way I Are (Dance with Somebody)\n| length1         = 3:03\n}}\n* '''Digital download'''<ref>{{cite web|title=iTunes - Music - The Way I Are (Dance With Somebody) [DallasK Remix] - Single by Bebe Rexha|url=https://itunes.apple.com/gb/album/the-way-i-are-dance-with-somebody-dallask-remix-single/id1263137502|publisher=[[iTunes Store]]}}</ref>\n{{Track listing\n| title1 = The Way I Are (Dance with Somebody)\n| note1 = DallasK Remix\n| length1 = 3:02\n}}\n\n== Charts ==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2017)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br /> position\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Australia ([[ARIA Charts|ARIA]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.auspop.com.au/2017/05/aria-chart-watch-422/|title=ARIA Chart Watch #422|publisher=auspOp|date=May 27, 2017|accessdate=May 27, 2017}}</ref>\n| 72\n|-\n{{singlechart|Wallonia Tip|10|artist=Bebe Rexha feat. Lil Wayne|song=The Way I Are (Dance with Somebody)|rowheader=true|accessdate=September 30, 2017}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Colombia ([[National-Report]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.national-report.com/top-colombia/|title=Top 100 Colombia|language=Spanish|publisher=[[National-Report]]|accessdate=July 22, 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170926183030/http://www.national-report.com:80/top-colombia/|archivedate=September 26, 2017}}</ref>\n| 97\n|-\n{{singlechart|Czechdigital|99|year=2017|week=24|rowheader=true|accessdate=Ju