zuela ([[National-Report]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.national-report.com/top-venezuela|title=Top 100 Venezuela|language=Spanish|publisher=[[National-Report]]|accessdate=May 8, 2018|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180508191332/http://www.national-report.com/top-venezuela/|archivedate=May 8, 2018}}</ref>\n| 7\n|}\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n{{Bebe Rexha}}\n{{Lil Wayne singles}}\n\n[[Category:2017 songs]]\n[[Category:2017 singles]]\n[[Category:Warner Records singles]]\n[[Category:Bebe Rexha songs]]\n[[Category:Lil Wayne songs]]\n[[Category:Songs written by Jacob Kasher]]\n[[Category:Songs written by Bebe Rexha]]\n[[Category:Music videos directed by Director X]]\n[[Category:Songs written by Lil Wayne]]\n[[Category:Songs written by Shannon Rubicam]]\n[[Category:Songs written by Jonas Jeberg]]\n[[Category:Songs written by Joel Little]]\n[[Category:Songs written by Clarence Coffee Jr.]]\n[[Category:Songs written by George Merrill (songwriter)]]\n[[Category:Song recordings produced by Joel Little]]\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Way I Are}}\n", "name_user": "2a01:e35:2e68:bca0:780d:3f67:dd20:76a6", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Way_I_Are_(Dance_with_Somebody)"}
{"title_page": "Twerk (City Girls song)", "text_new": "{{short description|2019 single by  City Girls featuring American rapper Cardi B}}\n{{Infobox song\n| name          = Twerk\n| cover         = City Girls featuring Cardi B - Twerk (Official Single Cover).png\n| type          = single\n| artist        = [[City Girls]] featuring [[Cardi B]]\n| album         = [[Girl Code (album)|Girl Code]]\n| released      = {{start date|2019|01|08}}\n| recorded      = 2018\n| format        =\n* [[Music download|Digital download]]\n* [[Streaming media|streaming]]\n| genre         = {{hlist|[[Miami bass]]|[[Bounce music|bounce]]}}\n| length        = 2:46\n| label         = \n* [[Quality Control Music|Quality Control]]\n* [[Motown Records|Motown]]\n* [[Capitol Records|Capitol]]\n| writer        = \n* [[Rico Love]]\n* [[Cardi B|Belcalis Almanzar]]\n* Raymond Sneed\n* [[Choppa|Darwin Turner]]\n* Caresha Brownlee\n* Jatavia Johnson\n| producer      =\n* Mr. Nova\n* Rico Love\n| chronology    = [[City Girls]]\n| prev_title    = [[I Just Wanna]]\n| prev_year     = 2018\n| next_title    = [[Caramel]]\n| next_year     = 2019\n| misc          = {{Extra chronology\n | artist       = [[Cardi B]]\n | type         = single\n | prev_title   = [[Money (Cardi B song)|Money]]\n | prev_year    = 2018\n | title        = Twerk\n | year         = 2019\n | next_title   = [[Please Me]]\n | next_year    = 2019\n }}\n{{External music video|{{YouTube|QryoOF5jEbc|\"Twerk\"}}}}\n}}\n\n\"'''Twerk'''\" is a song by American hip hop duo [[City Girls]] featuring American rapper [[Cardi B]], from the duo's album ''[[Girl Code (album)|Girl Code]]'' (2018). It was released to US [[rhythmic contemporary]] radio on January 8, 2019, as the album's lead single.<ref name=\"AllAccess\">{{Cite news |url=https://www.allaccess.com/top40-rhythmic/future-releases |title=Top 40 Rhythmic Future Releases |work=All Access |accessdate=January 18, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190106135635/https://www.allaccess.com/top40-rhythmic/future-releases |archive-date=January 6, 2019}}</ref> Filmed in [[Miami]], the song's music video was released the same month. \"Twerk\" is a New Orleans [[Bounce music|bounce]]-inspired song, which heavily samples [[Choppa]]'s \"Choppa Style\".<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.xxlmag.com/news/2019/01/city-girls-cardi-b-twerk-video/|title=City Girls and Cardi B Drop \"Twerk\" Video |last=Fitzgerald |first=Trent |date=January 16, 2018 |work=XXL |accessdate=January 18, 2018}}</ref> It also samples the popular [[Triggerman Beat]], which is prominent among the New Orleans [[Bounce music|bounce]] scene. It peaked at number 29 on the ''Billboard'' Hot 100 chart.<ref>https://www.billboard.com/charts/hot-100</ref>\n\n==Production==\n\"Twerk\" employs a xylophone sounding melody, hand claps and \"feverish\" snares.<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.hotnewhiphop.com/the-city-girls-release-booty-shaking-banger-twerk-new-song.1980986.html |title=The City Girls Release Booty Shaking Banger \"Twerk\" |work=HotNewHipHop |accessdate=January 26, 2019}}</ref> In her verse, Cardi references [[Jermaine Dupri]]'s \"[[Money Ain't a Thang]]\".<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.rap-up.com/2018/11/16/new-music-city-girls-cardi-b-twerk-remix/|title=City Girls feat. Cardi B - \"Twerk\" |work=Rap-Up |accessdate=January 26, 2019}}</ref>\n\n==Music video==\nDirected by [[Daps (director)|Daps]] and Sara Lacombe, the music video was filmed in [[Miami|Miami, Florida]] and released on January 16, 2019. The video shows Cardi B and Yung Miami [[Body painting|painted]] like a tiger and zebra, respectively, partying with a number of women on a [[yacht]]. In another location, at a construction site, they are joined by the top 20 finalists of the challenge sent by the City Girls, which consisted on finding \"the world's greatest twerker.\" The clip closes with the winner of the challenge.<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/city-girls-twerk-cardi-b-video-780144/ |title=Here\u2019s What It\u2019s Like to Watch City Girls\u2019 NSFW \u2018Twerk\u2019 Video in an Office |last=Holmes |first=Charles |date=January 16, 2018 |work=Rolling Stone |accessdate=January 18, 2018}}</ref> \n\nIn ''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]'' Carl Lamarre opined, \"the titillating video reaches its climax when the women hit the dirt and break into some next-level twerking. The mesermizing display will certainly drop some jaws, as both Cardi and Yung Miami redefine the meaning of twerk with their fun-filled visual.\"<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/hip-hop/8493857/city-girls-twerk-video-cardi-b|title=City Girls & Cardi B Show Off Their Elite Twerking Skills in 'Twerk' Video |last=Lamarre |first=Carl |date=January 16, 2018 |work=Billboard |accessdate=January 18, 2018}}</ref> ''[[Complex (magazine)|Complex]]''{{'}}s Sarah Montgomery stated \"this isn't your typical bad b*tches twerking to a banger music video.\"<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.complex.com/music/2019/01/city-girls-cardi-b-twerk-video|title=City Girls Recruits the Best Twerkers in the World for \"Twerk\" Video f/ Cardi B|website=Complex|accessdate=2019-04-10}}</ref> Meanwhile ''[[Entertainment Weekly]]''{{'}}s Shirley Li described the clip as \"incredible and hypnotic and very, very cheeky, in all senses of the word.\"<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://ew.com/music/2019/01/16/cardi-b-city-girls-twerk-twitter-reactions/ |title=Cardi B and City Girls new 'Twerk' video has Twitter in a tizzy \u2014 here are the funniest comments |last=Li |first=Shirley |date=January 16, 2019 |work=Entertainment Weekly |accessdate=January 25, 2019}}</ref>\n\n==Charts==\n===Weekly charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! Chart (2018\u201319)\n! Peak<br />position\n|-\n{{single chart|Canada|70|artist=Cardi B|rowheader=true|accessdate=January 29, 2019}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| New Zealand Hot Singles ([[Recorded Music NZ|RMNZ]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://nztop40.co.nz/chart/hotsingles?chart=4584|title=NZ Hot Singles Chart|publisher=[[Recorded Music NZ]]|date=January 28, 2019|accessdate=January 25, 2019}}</ref>\n| 31\n|-\n{{single chart|Billboardhot100|29|artist=Cardi B|rowheader=true|accessdate=January 29, 2019}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Billboardrandbhiphop|14|artist=Cardi B|rowheader=true|accessdate=January 23, 2019}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Billboardrhythmic|13|artist=Cardi B|rowheader=true|accessdate=March 26, 2019}}\n|}\n\n===Year-end charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2019)\n! scope=\"col\"| Position\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| US Hot R&B/Hip-Hop Songs (''Billboard'')<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2019/hot-r-and-and-b-hip-hop-songs|title=Hot R&B/Hip-Hop Songs \u2013 Year-End 2019|work=Billboard|accessdate=December 6, 2019}}</ref>\n| 57\n|}\n\n==Certifications==\n{{Certification Table Top}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=United States|type=single|artist=City Girls|title=Twerk|award=Platinum|digital=true|relyear=2018|certyear=2019|access-date=15 August 2019}}\n{{Certification Table Bottom|streaming=true}}\n\n==Release history==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Country\n! scope=\"col\"| Date\n! scope=\"col\"| Format\n! scope=\"col\"| Label\n! scope=\"col\"| Ref.\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| United States\n| January 8, 2019\n| [[Rhythmic contemporary]]\n| {{hlist|[[Miami bass]]|[[Bounce music|bounce]]}}\n| <ref name=\"AllAccess\"/>\n|-\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{YouTube|QryoOF5jEbc|Official Music Video}}\n\n{{Cardi B}}\n\n[[Category:2019 singles]]\n[[Category:City Girls songs]]\n[[Category:Cardi B songs]]\n[[Category:Capitol Records singles]]\n[[Category:Songs written by Cardi B]]\n[[Category:Songs written by Rico Love]]\n[[Category:2018 songs]]\n[[Category:Miami bass songs]]\n[[Category:Songs about buttocks]]\n[[Category:Songs about dancing]]\n