es of ''Finesse'', Atlantic Records and ASCAP.<ref name=\"Vynil\"/><ref name=\"ASCAP\">{{cite web|url=https://www.ascap.com/repertory#ace/search/workID/884659208|title=Finesse Cardi B Remix Credits \u2013 Ascap Work ID:894435667|publisher=[[American Society of Composers, Authors and Publishers|ASCAP]]|accessdate=October 5, 2019}}</ref>\n\n==Charts==\n{{col-start}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Weekly charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2018)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br /> position\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Argentina ([[Monitor Latino]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://charts.monitorlatino.com/top20/Argentina/General/20180219|publisher=Monitor Latino|accessdate=February 26, 2018|title=Top 20 Argentina \u2013 Del 19 al 26 de Febrero, 2018|language=Spanish|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180226212504/http://charts.monitorlatino.com/top20/Argentina/General/20180219|archive-date=February 26, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>\n| 17\n|-\n{{singlechart|Australia|6|artist=Bruno Mars feat. Cardi B|song=Finesse (Remix)|rowheader=true|accessdate=February 3, 2018|refname=\"AUS\"}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Austria|30|artist=Bruno Mars feat. Cardi B|song=Finesse (Remix)|rowheader=true|accessdate=January 17, 2018}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Flanders|8|artist=Bruno Mars feat. Cardi B|song=Finesse (Remix)|rowheader=true|accessdate=January 27, 2018|refname=\"Fla\"}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Wallonia|8|artist=Bruno Mars feat. Cardi B|song=Finesse (Remix)|rowheader=true|accessdate=March 23, 2018|refname=\"Wal\"}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Bolivia ([[Monitor Latino]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://charts.monitorlatino.com/top20/Bolivia/General/20180129|publisher=Monitor Latino|accessdate=January 17, 2018|title=Top 20 Bolivia \u2013 Del 29 de Enero al 4 de Febrero, 2018|language=Spanish|date=January 29, 2018|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180206073841/http://charts.monitorlatino.com/top20/Bolivia/General/20180129|archivedate=February 6, 2018|url-